{{main|月球方格列表|月面座標}}
[[月面座標|月面座標]]用來標示月球表面上的位置。[[國際天文學聯合會|國際天文學聯合會]]建議用"平地球/極軸"系統<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://astrogeology.usgs.gov/Projects/WGCCRE/WGCCRE2003preprint.pdf |title=IAU/IAG Working Group on Cartographic Coordinates and Rotational Elements: 2003 |access-date=2011-10-31 |archive-date=2011-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111024101841/http://astrogeology.usgs.gov/Projects/WGCCRE/WGCCRE2003preprint.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[本初子午線|本初子午線]]穿过地月中心连线<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://lunar.gsfc.nasa.gov/library/451-SCI-000958.pdf |title=A Standardized Lunar Coordinate System for the Lunar Reconnaissance Orbiter |access-date=2011-10-31 |archive-date=2020-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808005810/https://lunar.gsfc.nasa.gov/library/451-SCI-000958.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。以[[莫斯汀|莫斯汀]]撞击坑的中心{{Coord|0.7|S|5.88|W|globe:Moon|nogoogle=1|noosm=1}}作為定義月面座標的基準點。[[美国地质调查局|美国地质调查局]]把[[月球|月球]]划分为多块区域：在1:2,500,000比例尺的地图上划分为30个[[月球方格列表|方格]]<ref>{{cite web| url=http://astrogeology.usgs.gov/Projects/PlanetaryMapping/Lunar/| title=Lunar Geologic Mapping| publisher=NASA/USGS Planetary Geologic Mapping Program| date=2007-09-19| accessdate=2007-12-09| archive-date=2013-02-17| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130217125715/http://astrogeology.usgs.gov/Projects/PlanetaryMapping/Lunar/| dead-url=no}}</ref>，在1:1,000,000比例尺的地图上划分为144个方格。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/dAtlas.html |title=USGS Astrogeology: Gazetteer of Planetary Nomenclature - USGS Digital Atlas of the Moon<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2011-11-29 |archive-date=2008-07-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080704170439/http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/dAtlas.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
